data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Belleau Ridge subdivision, nestled in the heart of Ooltewah. This meticulously crafted residence boasts timeless charm and modern elegance, offering a perfect blend of comfort and sophistication.    Step inside and be greeted by the inviting ambiance of solid hardwood flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the main level and into the primary bedroom. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring rich wood cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a large island, and a stylish tile backsplash.    Entertain guests in the expansive 2-story great room, adorned with a gas log fireplace accented by charming stone details. 60' inch TV hung above fireplace is included with the sell.  he adjacent sunroom is a tranquil retreat, offering engineered hardwood flooring, stunning floor-to-ceiling windows, and remote-control shades for year-round enjoyment.    Work from home in style in the main level office space, complete with coffered ceilings and glass double door entry. The primary suite on the main level provides a luxurious sanctuary, boasting a spa-like bathroom with a jetted bathtub, double vanities, a step-in tile shower, and a large walk-in closet.    Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms, an oversized bonus room that doubles as a fourth bedroom [contains closet], and a loft area overlooking the great room below. The second level also features a full bathroom with double vanity, perfect for accommodating family and guests.    Outside, the enchanting backyard oasis awaits, featuring a gorgeous open deck overlooking lush green lawn and mature privacy trees. A large storage area tucked away under the deck and sunroom provides ample space for lawn equipment, tools, or yard games.    With its charming stone and cement fiber siding exterior, decorative shutters, and dark bronze exterior light fixtures, this well-maintained home offers curb appeal that stands out. Move-in ready and meticulously maintained, this home is ready to welcome you with open arms.  Don't miss your chance to make it yours. Schedule your showing today!
